   A *UIElement* takes a whole line on the LCD, a render method returns the text to render on screen, an @latex {on\_event} method handles events to consume graphics interactions, a boolean value is returned to specify if the component requires internal focus.

   @code (language=rust, label=lst:graphics-element) codes/graphics/element.txt\

   Below, the button component is reported as an example.

   @code (language=rust, label=lst:graphics-button) codes/graphics/button.txt\

